-- ViniPortugal's Vale Discusses Portuguese Wines (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-07-02T12:23:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-02/viniportugal-s-vale-discusses-portuguese-wines-audio-.html
Nuno Vale, chief marketing officer 
for ViniPortugal, discusses the rise in popularity of Portuguese
wines. Vale talks with Bloomberg's Courtney Donohoe and Joe 
Brusuelas on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock."  They are joined 
by Ben Willis, managing director at Albert Fried & Co. LLC, and 
 Les Funtleyder , president of Poliwogg's Investment Advisory 
division.
 (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:13
 